reviews.text:
This was a great remix. My rating had nothing to do with the original. Thus tastes great, but I think the juicy peach is slightly over powering in the mix, even after a steep. I'll be making this again and just lowering the peach, this has made it into my small rotation! &#xD;
&#xD;
Update on this, I left half of my 30mL for a few months and came back to it. The peach finally settled down enough for me to not dominate the rest of the mix. The ginger came out much more and this is an amazing me now. For me, the steep was too short and it caused the peach to be VERY dominate and overpower the others. My assumption is after a month steep it hit where I wanted it to for personal tastes. This was amazing after a longer steep to my taste.
